data.description: Beautiful hilltop country home setting on nearly an acre with beautiful views in all directions!  This 3 bedroom, 2 baths has many updates.  From drive you can enter the family room with entrance to dining room and flows into kitchen.  You can set at breakfast bar that extends into family room to drink your morning coffee and enjoy the outside country view.  The living area is very large with wood burning fireplace for back up heat or just enjoy in the winter.  The utility room is plenty of big for extra frig, freezer and has a sink.  Down the hall is first remodeled bath with tub and shower. The primary bedroom has two closets and remodeled bath with large shower and double sinks vanity. 2 additional large bedrooms off hall.  Outside between family room & garage is wood deck to enjoy your outside grilling.  There is a dog pen on southside of the house as well as front yard is fenced too.  Several large trees in the front and back yards.  Come to the country, just 18 miles from Paris.
